      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NIELSEN PARK (3) resumes and now in the Mack Griffith yard. Failed to fire first-up from the outside draw last campaign with a battling eighth over 1200m at Sale on May 3. Maps well for this and the booking of Aaron Bullock is a good guide to his chances. SEDDUKE (5) four-year-old Magna Garcia entire from Dats A Lass on debut for the Julia Presits camp. Trained on the track and will prove hard to catch after his slick 1000m trial win at Scone. BUMBLING ARTIE (2) snagged back from the outside gate and like the way he closed off when a close third over 1010m at Moruya. Ready to peak and the winkers go on. Genuine top-three player. THREE WISHES (10) resumes from a lengthy spell. Showed ability in her two career minor placings and finds a winnable race today. Primed with the two trials and must be kept safe.",
